To use the HTML Minification for Razor, you have to change your Web.config to replace the default ASP.NET MVC factory by the Meleze's one:

<pre>
<configuration>
  <system.web.webPages.razor>
    <host factoryType="Meleze.Web.Razor.MinifyHtmlWebRazorHostFactory,Meleze.Web.Razor" />
  </system.web.webPages.razor>
</configuration>
</pre>

You can find more details in <a href="http://cestdumeleze.net/blog/2011/minifying-the-html-with-asp-net-mvc-and-razor/">Minifying HTML With ASP.NET MVC And Razor</a>.

